== Tagruppit<ref>https://www.google.com/search?q=Tagruppit&oq=Tagruppit&aqs=chrome..69i57j0i13l6j69i60.2797j1j4&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8</ref> : ==
Tagruppit tga ula nttat yan wanaw iẓlin uẓawan amaziɣ, assaɣ ns iwckad sg yat taguri [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tfransist]] : "Group" (Tarabbut); anaw ad ar bahra ittili g tmɣriw d tfugliwin n tawjiwin. Nzzḍaṛ a nini mas anaw ad iga yan wanaw n uẓawan amaynu nɣ atrar.

Tagruppit ar gis ttilin kullu imassn n uẓawan zund [[Lbanju]], [[Tallunt]], [[Ribab|Rribab]] ... ar tigira.
