==Aḥidus<ref>Amzaray ingr Aḥidus d Taḥidust : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4hYUfPLZ8fg</ref><ref>https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ahidous</ref><ref>http://www.ich.gov.jo/sites/default/files/ldllt_lsymyyy.pdf</ref> : ==
Aḥidus (Aḥidus maci Taḥidust acku imzaray uḥidus f Taḥidust) iga yan wanaw iẓlin n uẓawan amaziɣ, illa wanaw ad g tmazirt n [[Ẓayan|Ayt Ẓayan.]] Aḥidus g tizwiri iga yan wanaw n udraz (adraz) g [[Aṭlas anammas|waṭlas anammas]], mass tusutin f tusutin iwrri iga yan wanaw g uẓawan. Aḥidus ar tetturar tarabbut n tmɣarin nɣ n irgazn. Aḥidus dars anamk n "''ini tamdyazt nɣ tanḍḍamt s urar d adraz''". 

Aẓawan ad tyussant srs [[Aɣrf|iɣrfan]] n [[Ayt Ɛmṛ]] d [[Ayt iccu]] d [[Ayt Ḥatm]], g waṭlas anammas.

